				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "1) Players get close to arguing nobles in the dining room CTY_Main_A -248; 25; -51\r\n2)Interact with any of the nobles, then follow them outside\r\n3) Interact with a noble during the AD\r\n4) End second dialog and have them fight or leave\r\n5) Talk to Noble 2"
				},
